Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.27,0:00:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.90,0:00:14.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:14.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.16,0:00:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.92,0:00:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.04,0:00:37.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:37.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
