Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:59.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(398.554,494)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:02.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741.031,160)}免费沙拉台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:02.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(743.034,726)}不收费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630.877,984)}来跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:24.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1013.409,146)}免费沙拉台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:24.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(923.284,914)}不收费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:33.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360.501,682)}免费
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.27,0:01:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连免费沙拉台都招呼不到客人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If a free salad bar doesn't bring in customers
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有啥能招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what will?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.07,0:01:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里需要有一些变动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's going to be some changes around here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(949,920)}零 钱
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A customer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  无微不至关照他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, cater to his every whim
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回可别搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and don't screw this one up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎登船  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在蟹堡王这里  您就是船长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here at the Krusty Krab, you are the Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我是您船上的佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I am your cabin boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倘若您颇有微词
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just say the word
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.27,0:02:06.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就自觉去关禁闭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:06.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I will throw myself in the brig
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能为您点餐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想换零钱打公用电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was change for the pay phone
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生的零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Monsieur's changez"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.03,0:02:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.36,0:02:19.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:19.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可能也注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you may have noticed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本月利润严重下滑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,profits are way down this month
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要来个营销噱头吸引顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need a gimmick to bring in customers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个旱鸭子有什么办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you lubbers have any ideas?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l've got one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每笔消费附赠一双免费袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a free pair of socks with every purchase
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或许可以来  午夜双堡疯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Double-Patty Midnight Madness
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满嘴蛤蜊日行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about Mouthful of Clams Day?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁要是满嘴塞着蛤蜊过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone who shows up with a mouthful of clams
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能领取免费饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gets a free drink
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.32,0:03:03.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我考虑的是现场表演之类的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was thinking more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,along the lines of live entertainment
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.83,0:03:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现场表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a floor show
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是才艺表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a talent show
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主持人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your host
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个时刻是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the moment I've
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.54,0:03:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说我们  一直梦寐以求的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, we've been dreaming of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想看  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以把文化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will be responsible for bringing culture
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带到所谓裤头村的这片文化沙漠里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into this cultural wasteland we call Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更不用说钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And not to mention the money
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The money?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就可以预见到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can see it now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你女儿珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your daughter, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会变得名声响亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Her name up in lights
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little Pearlie
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a star?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopping clams
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才艺表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A talent show
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特有才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talented
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得打电话叫爸妈来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd better call the folks
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you've got a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我家闺女变成明星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make my little girl a star
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我要什么时候上台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, what time am I going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going on what?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上台表演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The show
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么时候要上台表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When am I going on the show?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有样很厉害的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a great act
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敢问你有什么才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What talent could you possibly possess?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.69,0:04:17.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:17.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连你爸妈都不会想看那玩意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one, not even your parents would want to see that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家想看的是文化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the people want is culture
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是会跳舞的泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not dancing bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要构思出史上最有文化的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm going to come up with the most cultured act ever
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙唯一有文化的地方就是网球鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only culture that guy has is in his tennis shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(619,920)}培养真菌
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.18,0:04:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,网球鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tennis shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I crack myself up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在在蟹堡王才艺表演的现场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are live at the Krusty Krab talent show
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为大家呈现顶尖的才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,featuring the finest talent
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,座无虚席
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A full house
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸妈来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's Mom and Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们会特骄傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They are going to be so proud
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  我是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I like money
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get ready
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, listen up, people, listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gather around, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.28,0:05:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chop chop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可能会觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you may be thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你们大红大紫的唯一机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is your one shot at the big time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这机会是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  表演这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squid, how about this for the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:23.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(951.323,732)}吸水先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神奇的吸水先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The amazing Mr. Absorbency
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人想看你吸水膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one is going to want to see you engorge yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我上台表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let me be in the show
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会做任何事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何事  任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,anything, anything
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说你真的要参加表演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you really want to be in the show?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  表演完了你就去拖地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you get to mop up afterwards
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别来烦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, will you stop bugging me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这种感受就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, this is what it feels like
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大红大紫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the big time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了这个拖把  我就能重塑我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With this mop, I shape my destiny
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  欢欢迎观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, and-and welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一届一年一度章鱼哥才艺表演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the first annual Squidward Tentacles talent show
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本表演赞助者为蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sponsored by the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡之家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,home of the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为不会有别人会给这玩意一个家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because no one else would give it a home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our next act
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充分证明了走后门现象依然猖獗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is living proof that nepotism is alive and well
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nepoti
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位鳍声有请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your fins together for
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.44,0:07:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的闺女终于变成明星了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My little girl is finally a star
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a K-r-u
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a s-t-y
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫做才艺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's what I call talent
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My legs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说要怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.64,0:07:43.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拖地应不应该前后拖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:43.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I mop, should I go forward and back?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.23,0:07:43.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:43.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从左到右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,side to side
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来是诗歌朗诵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, poetry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朗诵者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真是字字珠玑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He has such a way with words
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊快啊  大诗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, Ginsberg
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再不赶紧念完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't hurry it up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就没时间上演压轴好戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're not going to have enough time for the best act
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.88,0:08:14.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  该用清洁先生还是干净博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:14.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, should I use Mr. Cleanser or Dr. Clean?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.14,0:08:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1055.468,702)}神奇浮游生物
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.97,0:08:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  神奇浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, The Amazing Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要用这套魔术戏法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the use of prestidigitation
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.23,0:08:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在你们眼皮底下让一个蟹黄堡消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will make a Krabby Patty disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before your very eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  我需要一位观众自愿配合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, I'll need a volunteer from the audience
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你演完了  小东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your act's over, bub
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次姑且让你赢一回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may win this time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瞬间转移
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shee-ah kazing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧下台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off the stage
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场表演烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This show is a disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是要毁了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ruining me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦蟹老板  放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't you worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特别留了最佳节目做压轴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l've saved the best for last
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll see
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看在你份上  希望你没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For your sake, I hope you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们期盼的时刻终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the moment you've all been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们留了最好的节目压轴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've saved the best for last
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.74,0:09:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位掌声有请无与伦比章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your hands together for
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the incomparable Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:25.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.972,168)\clip(580.808,92,696.969,166)}章鱼哥秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:26.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.972,168)\clip(698.972,90,761.058,168)}章鱼哥秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.972,168)\clip(576.802,96,757.053,170)}章鱼哥秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:28.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.972,168)}章鱼哥秀
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(999.13,150)}免费沙拉台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:49.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017.805,830)}不收费
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样下去我会亏钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm losing money on this deal
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每分钱都值得花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's worth every penny
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些臭鱼烂虾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bottom feeders
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全不懂才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't even know talent
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.33,0:10:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No talent
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我现在能上台了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, can I go on now?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  演完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, show's over
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还真的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's really not too bad
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.02,0:10:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.11,0:10:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want more
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们要我返场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They want an encore
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站一边去  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand aside, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want more
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场表演真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a great show
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我儿子是明星了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My son's a star
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道他竟然有这般才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who ever knew he had such talent?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要再来一辆手推车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be needing another wheelbarrow
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备下周的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for next week's show
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.23\pos(318.504,317.334)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:57.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424.098,678)\frz18.85}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.39\pos(455.972,275.333)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(290.613,326)\frz22.28}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz22.28\pos(464.027,614)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420.195,494)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.99,0:12:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的午餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lunchtime at The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都在享用着蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everyone enjoying their Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找得到吗  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you spot her, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那里  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down there, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来发生了一场蟹黄堡绑架案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There appears to be a Krabby Patty-napping in progress
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凶手只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There can be only one culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478.889,507.333)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利总算是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, victory is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了  我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win, I win
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他逃走了  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He got away, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他最终还是偷走了我的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's finally stolen me secret recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可未必  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps not, Monsieur Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.83,0:12:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为还有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for it's
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's far enough
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:39.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.004,744.667)}魔术店
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有没有看到个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多有这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about this tall, and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(993.794,694)}魔术店
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是魔术店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A magic shop
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是魔术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you a magician?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一次  我见到这么个魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One time I saw this magician
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他做了这个  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he did this thing, a-and he
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之他就跟咱说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, and then he told us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"if you believe in yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.82,0:14:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要有一小撮魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"and with a tiny pinch of magic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你所有梦想都会成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all your dreams can come true"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  这些年来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, and after all these years
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为我就是折磨大师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l thought I was the master of torture
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样太没理了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that just wasn't fair
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿走这个破蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take the stupid patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我也不要秘密配方了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l don't want the secret recipe anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.89,0:14:34.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计我餐厅不会有蟹堡王那么成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess my restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will never be as good as the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772.358,736.667)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是不知道当废物是个什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know what it's like to be a loser
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,振作起来  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得你是赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说你是个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said you're a
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.45,0:14:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当裤头村公敌感觉怎么样啊  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be the most hated thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Bikini Bottom, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.08,0:14:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:14:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  为了庆祝成功赶走你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and for running you out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要给这个小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're going to make this kid
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,授予今日裤头村荣誉好小子称号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,honorary town rookie of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.96,0:15:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他是一个好小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For he's a jolly good rookie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:11.26,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自歌曲"For He's a Jolly Good Fellow" ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.26,0:15:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他是一个好小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For he's a jolly good rookie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只要有一个朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet if he had just one friend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就肯定不会这么坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't be such a meanie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.27,0:15:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有人会否认这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which nobody
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772.358,736.667)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A customer?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今天的特餐是海霸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our special today is chum
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什锦饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,balaya
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.58,0:15:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天害我丢脸丢得还不够大发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Haven't you degraded me enough for one day?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要你出来跟我玩一玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l want you to come out and play with me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Play
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会引起热核反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know how to induce thermonuclear fusion?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  可我喜欢跟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, but I like to go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个幼稚方块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That naive cube
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还得受多长时间的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long must I suffer this?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是没有让他走开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not letting him leave, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是复仇的大好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect opportunity for revenge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说详细点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elaborate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟海绵宝宝交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Befriend the SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后等到时机刚刚好  就带走蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, when the time is just right, take the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去  小天才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get moving, genius
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别让他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't let him get away
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友到水母田里捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fishing with my friends in Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我会玩你的小游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob, I'll play your little game
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一个到水母田的是臭蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Last one to the fields is a rotten clam
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  我来拿大网
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, I get the big net
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来拿小网
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you get the little net
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃了水母会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happens after we eat them?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是吃水母  要这样捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't eat them, you catch them, like this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就把水母放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you throw them back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.48,0:16:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过要小心触手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but watch out for stingers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,触手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stingers?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全天下都得向痞老板下跪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All knees will bow to Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hail, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了  我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win, I win
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点不在于输赢  在于快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not about winning, it's about fun
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是啥东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快乐就是你在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun is when you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.05,0:17:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快乐就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun is
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.88,0:17:13.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:13.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kind of
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点像是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sort of like a
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快乐是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你拼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me spell it for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,F表示朋友  一起同甘共苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"F" is for friends who do stuff together
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.10,0:17:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,U表示你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"U" is for you and me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,N表示无论何时无论何地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"N" is for anywhere and anytime at all
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这蓝蓝深海里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down here in the deep blue sea
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(294.803,774)}快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,F表示放火  烧掉整座镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"F" is fire that burns down the whole town
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,U表示原子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"U" is for uranium
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bombs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.45,0:17:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,N表示无人生还  到时你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"N" is for no survivors when you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  这些可不是快乐的内涵所在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, those things aren't what fun is all about
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, do it like this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,F表示朋友  一起同甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"F" is for friends who
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全白痴得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's completely idiotic
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, let me help you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,F表示朋友  一起同甘共苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"F" is for friends who do stuff together
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,U表示你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"U" is for you and me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,N表示无论何时无论何地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"N" is for anywhere and anytime at all
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这蓝蓝深海里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down here in the deep blue sea
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I don't understand this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得我内心麻麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel all tingly inside
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该停下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should we stop?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.27,0:18:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不该停  你有这种感觉才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's how you're supposed to feel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I like it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,F表示嬉戏  在这花田里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"F" is for frolic through all the flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,U表示尤克里里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"U" is for ukulele
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,N表示挑鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"N" is for nose picking
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分泡泡糖  舔沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sharing gum and sand licking
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我好兄弟一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here with my best buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:38.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940.436,774)}快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叛变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mutiny
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700.325,747.333)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.60,0:18:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And after that
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就在花田里嬉戏  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we frolicked through the flowers and then we
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最快乐的那部分是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the really fun part was when we
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷蟹黄堡的事情你都干了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you do with the Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patty, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这事是急不得的  懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't rush these things, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都把任务忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're forgetting the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388.54,588)}秘方
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都要被同化了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going native, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有好些时候没看到痞老板了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Plankton for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他肯定是在密谋什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He must be scheming
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半洗心革面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's changed
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you knows
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1049.82,384.667)}快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说他洗心革面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's changed, I tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板兄弟  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton buddy, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了这里是禁友区
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot this is a no-friends zone
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.93,0:19:29.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:29.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能借一步说话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,may I speak to you in private?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.85,0:19:36.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不介意我把这玩意放这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:36.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't mind if I set this here, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是要干嘛  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this all about, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是个贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a thief
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看他眼里的欲望  他要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look at the lust in his eye, he's
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你咋就不能接受我们的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just accept our friendship?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他目的是我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just after me recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会给你证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll prove it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你大老远走过来一定是饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry after that long walk over here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.50,0:19:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  不过我要留点胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I'm saving my appetite
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去电影院吃爆米花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for some popcorn at the movies
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们受够你那些小测试了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've had enough of your little tests, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  我们出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Plankton, let's get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许那小子说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe the lad was right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许痞老板改过自新了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe Plankton's gone straight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许太阳要打西边出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And maybe scallops will fly out of my pants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on there, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm a-comin'
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢续集  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure like sequels, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王  你坐到我朋友身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, bubble bass, you're sitting on my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, bubble bass
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.89,0:20:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.35,0:20:50.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他这是在骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's deceiving you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.81,0:20:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把手伸进他口袋  拿出里面的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reach into his pocket now, and take what he's got
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也一样  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, too, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, then?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说你眼前这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you see here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.91,0:21:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么会没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you not see it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I see it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不就是个蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a Krabby Patty, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们明明唱了快乐歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we sang the fun song
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得我要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to be sick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,久什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你密谋做这事多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long were you planning on doing this?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.90,0:21:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是骗了你才把蟹黄堡弄到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l tricked you to get the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你却向我示出了友情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then you showed me friendship
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I realize
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那才是我真正想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's all I ever really wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.08,0:21:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才怪  假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not really
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当恶人可快乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being evil is too much fun
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  这世间一切都无法拆散我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darling, I knew nothing would ever tear us apart
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, he's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.60,0:22:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他偷到了蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He got the patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He won
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.89,0:22:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.27,0:22:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道银幕后边是什么不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you know what's behind these screens?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实心混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Solid concrete
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.70,0:22:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为痞老板洗心革面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought Plankton had changed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别怪他  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't blame him, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.41,0:22:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切友谊都遭不住蟹黄堡的诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No friendship can withstand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the allure of a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回蟹堡王去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来份新鲜蟹黄堡  我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and have a fresh one, on me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.04,0:22:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.88,0:22:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是只打个折算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe at a discount
